":"要救依家既兒登<br />\n<br />\n一定有地方要連登admin配合<br />\n否則  會員係唔會做到咩 <br />\n<br />\n同埋， 係會員喺度討論，多唔多三毛分化，  admin 可能根本無意去管<br />\n<br />\n所以如果admin無表示， 基本上極難推行救兒登行動"},{"pid":"0604a5194755243e83500c4260f5ceb751373a45","tid":1234290,"uid":29093,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"仲有其實都唔係新會員問題<br />\n<br />\n新會員 憑編號就睇到<br />\n<br />\n問題係 26xxxx前邊 26 萬個account <br />\n有太多搞事既account <br />\nblock極都有，  可見滲入程度非常嚴重。"},{"pid":"a5cbe7b05a741b2dd4cdc3517fcac3525c2eea70","tid":1234290,"uid":106851,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"推，依家啲正負皮去得好快<br />\n佢哋淨正皮啲分化post唔留comment我哋跟本防唔到"},{"pid":"4a6998e35479f6fa83e3cfe92c9b1de952fc88a0","tid":1234290,"uid":377,"like":4,"dislike":23,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"做咩唔比我註冊？"},{"pid":"75e0a4ff171dfc90fd3146d03f260615cd57f6a9","tid":1234290,"uid":209890,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"同你講<br />\n連登你已經無回頭路<br />\n作為市民網絡基地<br />\n今日場仗你唔出力一齊打<br />\n日後中共第一個清算你"},{"pid":"e3d9c0586196b04740076ec8ad9e0adf60449114","tid":1234290,"uid":40369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"會員數係連登一個重大數字，會唔會畀註冊<br />\n但要三個月/登入數夠幾多日先畀發文/留言"},{"pid":"77a4b011a077904aad987e2847020c712556b9ca","tid":1234290,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"跪求連仔馬上停止新會員註冊"},{"pid":"c0dc3cf251226fefcc82f459a922e972683ede4f","tid":1234290,"uid":145292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"停止新會員註冊"},{"pid":"973c7bb32113028e3b51106b8535ae6994489ac6","tid":1234290,"uid":145292,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"停止新會員註冊"},{"pid":"4a3446af84b9f0ce4a806de921fc7b349f0665b9","tid":1234290,"uid":5800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:35:0